{
  "texts": [
    "For example, majority of the generated polymers possess linear backbones and contain the \"-O-CH2-CH2-\" fragment within their chains.",
    "Given the high ionic conductivity of PEO-like polymers, such an observation is to be expected.",
    "Beyond conditioning polymer generation on conductivity, we can also design polymer electrolytes with specific functional groups.",
    "By strategically designing these groups, we can offer valuable guidance for easier experimental synthesis, such as proposing potential precursors and reaction pathways.",
    "In addition, this approach allows us to incorporate specific functional groups based on domain knowledge or avoid those that result in undesirable properties for polymer electrolytes."
  ]
}